struct.exostring:
Player can talk to Gadon and get information about Bastila. Gadon tells player to find the missing prototype and bring it back if they want to enter the swoop race.
This sets Tar_MissLook to 1, which will activate the Mission triggers in the Undercity.
When the player returns with the swoop engine the game will transition to the Bek cutscene before the swoop race.

There will be several Mission triggers, though none in the Outcast Village
